{"arkId":"cl010113644","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010113644","modified ":"2025-09-04","title":"Un vase d\u0027une paire (OA 10984)","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Un vase d\u0027une paire (OA 10984)"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : vers 1750","currentLocation":"Sully, [OArt] Salle 611 - Jean-Fran\u00e7ois Oeben","room":"Salle 611, Aile Aile Sully, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1750,"endYear":"","imprecision":"vers","text":"","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Manufacture de Meissen","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q76941091"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 10985","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"vase, r\u00e9cipient","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Vase \u00e0 corps renfl\u00e9 d\u00e9cor\u00e9 de fleurs et de fruits en relief d\u0027o\u00f9 s\u0027\u00e9chappent deux poign\u00e9es en forme de brins d\u0027herbe. Le d\u00e9cor peint se compose, sur une face, de sc\u00e8nes avec des personnages, et, sur l\u0027autre, d\u0027oiseaux sur fond blanc.\r\nLe d\u00e9cor de ces vases est une synth\u00e8se des styles qui pr\u00e9dominaient \u00e0 Meissen au milieu du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle : des sc\u00e8nes galantes dans le go\u00fbt fran\u00e7ais y voisinent, en effet, avec des repr\u00e9sentations naturalistes d\u0027oiseaux et d\u0027insectes. L\u0027aspect le plus extraordinaire de ces vases reste cependant le d\u00e9cor de fleurs et de fruits en relief qui sont l\u0027expression d\u0027une tendance apparue vers 1740. Peut-\u00eatre pourrait-on voir dans ce go\u00fbt pour la plastique l\u0027influence de J.J. K\u00e4ndler, bien que d\u00e8s 1715 d\u00e9j\u00e0 on ait employ\u00e9, d\u0027une fa\u00e7on beaucoup plus timide cependant, ce proc\u00e9d\u00e9 d\u00e9coratif.\r\nC\u0027est au milieu du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle \u00e9galement que la manufacture de Meissen connut son plus grand rayonnement ; elle servit notamment de source d\u0027inspiration \u00e0 la manufacture de Vincennes.","inscriptions":"Inscription : \r ; deux \u00e9p\u00e9es entrecrois\u00e9es (peintes en bleu)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"18","displayDimension":"18 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"13","displayDimension":"13 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"9","displayDimension":"9 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"6,8","displayDimension":"6,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":12,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : porcelaine dure\r\nTechnique : techniques c\u00e9ramique","placeOfCreation":"Meissen = Mei\u00dfen (Allemagne-\u003ESaxe)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection Charles Pasteur (1870-191) ; legs, Henriette Pasteur (1895-1984), 1984","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"M. Pasteur, Charles","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"},{"value":"Mme Pasteur, Henriette","note":" (Veuve de Charles Pasteur)","role":", Collectionneur ; Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"legs","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date du legs","value":"1984","startYear":1984,"endYear":1984},{"type":"date de l\u0027arr\u00eat\u00e9","value":"16\/02\/1985","startYear":1985,"endYear":1985}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement d